summary: An Ordinance accepting a deed of conveyance from Elizabeth M. McGilvra, Oliver C. McGilvra, Lillian L. McGilvra, Carrie E. Burke, and Oliver C. McGilvra and Charles L. Denny as executors of the last will and estate of John J. McGilvra deceased, to a part of Lot One (1), Block "G", A. A. Denny's Addition to the City of Seattle.
